<br />As long as it doesn't negatively impact game play like in The Lord of the Rings, better sound is a good thing. A song like "One Winged Angel" from FFVII ("<a href="http://magiccheese.ytmnd.com/" class="postlink">Bells frogs Bing cherries jingle bells ham and cheese SEPHIROTH!</a>") could have been done on the Super NES. ("SEPHIROTH!")

		

