	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />It's a joke about the quality and general sound of the lyrics. They are latin and you can find a rough translation of what they are saying. But if you look at the lyrics (Bells Frogs, etc) and listen it really does sound like it could be that.
<br />
<br />FF7 works similar to older consoles in that the sound processor uses samples to play the song rather than just streaming music from the disc since the disc must be free to load assets while in battle as every single asset cannot fit into memory at once. There is a trick to exploit this behavior too. You cast Regen on your party and then another spell and after regen is cast you open the CD lid and the battle will not proceed until it can load the new spell so you can regenerate all your health without fear of being attacked.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
